aches. Concurrently, hardware advancements following Moore''s Law have created ecosystems where parallel processing capabilities exceed the capacity of traditional sequential programming models to', 'b837db1c-7de8-4844-a9e7-2d793ad26fd4', '1001', 'ORD-YAN-3919');
